    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.學生明列學習標的<br>2.學生闡述學習標的選取理由<br>3.師生共同討論學習計畫<br>4.學生依計畫自主學習<br>5.師生共同討論盤點學習成效<br>6.教師完成評定成績<br>",
        "en": "1.The student set the study goals<br>2.The students explain why are the study goals selected<br>3.A study plan is constructed as a result of bilateral discussions by the student and the instructor<br>4.The student carry out the study plan<br>5.The student and the instructor review the performances<br>6.The instructor give the final grade<br>"
    },
